<lb n="0707a05"/><p>行者應了了諦觀。不久當見清淨菩提心。離
<lb n="0707a06"/>諸塵垢淨如滿月。即誦菩提心真言曰</p>
<lb n="0707a07"/><p type="dharani">唵冒地質多母怛跛<note place="inline">二合引</note>那夜<note n="0707001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【乙】</note><app n="0707001"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>彌</p>
<lb n="0707a08"/><p>想菩提月中有曇字。如金色輝曜。如日放大
<lb n="0707a09"/>光明。便即變成般若波羅蜜劍。離諸分別能
<lb n="0707a10"/>斷煩惱。想為智劍真言曰</p>
<lb n="0707a11"/><p type="dharani">唵底瑟&CB00109;<note place="inline">二合</note>渴&CB00344;</p>
<lb n="0707a12"/><p>想其智劍漸漸增大遍周法界真言曰</p>
<lb n="0707a13"/><p type="dharani">唵娑頗<note place="inline">二合</note>囉渴&CB00344;</p>
<lb n="0707a14"/><p>想其智劍漸漸收攝等自身量真言曰</p>
<lb n="0707a15"/><p type="dharani">唵僧賀囉渴&CB00344;</p>
<lb n="0707a16"/><p>為令智劍堅固不散復誦真言曰</p>
<lb n="0707a17"/><p type="dharani">唵涅哩<note place="inline">二合</note>荼底瑟&CB00109;<note place="inline">二合</note>渴&CB00344;</p>
<lb n="0707a18"/><p>想空中如來盡入智劍同為一體。作是思惟。
<lb n="0707a19"/>如彼諸佛體性我亦同然真言曰</p>
<lb n="0707a20"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">三</note>麼喻<note place="inline">引</note>含摩訶<note place="inline">引</note>三<note n="0707002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩＝麼【乙】＊</note><app n="0707002"><lem>摩</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">麼</rdg></app>喻<note place="inline">引</note>含薩&CB00085;怛他
<lb n="0707a21"/>&CB00617;多鼻<note n="0707003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＝三【乙】</note><app n="0707003"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">三</rdg></app><note place="inline">去</note>&CB00155;<note place="inline">引</note>地渴&CB00344;怛麼<note place="inline">二合</note>句<note place="inline">引</note>含</p>
<lb n="0707a22"/><p>想其智劍漸漸變成文殊師利童真菩薩。具
<lb n="0707a23"/>大威德身著種種瓔珞。頂想五髻。右手持智
<lb n="0707a24"/>劍。左手執青蓮花。花上<note n="0707004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔有〕－【乙】</note><app n="0707004"><lem>有</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>般若波羅蜜經
<lb n="0707a25"/>夾。身色如&CB00614;金。心誦阿<note n="0707005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＝羅【乙】</note><app n="0707005"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">羅</rdg></app>跛者曩一遍</p>
<lb n="0707a26"/><lg><l>次結金剛智劍印</l><l>止觀相叉作滿月</l>
<lb n="0707a27"/><l>忍願皆&CB00594;如劍形</l><l>印心及<note n="0707006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">額＝顛【乙】</note><app n="0707006"><lem>額</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">顛</rdg></app>喉頂上</l>
<lb n="0707a28"/><l>即成護身堅本尊</l></lg>
<lb n="0707a29"/><p>真言曰</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1171.0707b" n="0707b"/>
<lb n="0707b01"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底乞叉拏<note place="inline">三合</note>地瑟&CB00109;<note place="inline">二合</note>娑&CB00085;
<lb n="0707b02"/><note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00805;</p>
<lb n="0707b03"/><lg><l>次當灌頂結寶印</l><l>二手相叉作為月</l>
<lb n="0707b04"/><l>進力反屈如寶形</l><l>禪智二度下相捻</l>
<lb n="0707b05"/><l>置於額上分兩邊</l><l>便結智拳如<note n="0707007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">繫＝擊【乙】</note><app n="0707007"><lem>繫</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">擊</rdg></app>帛</l>
<lb n="0707b06"/><l>兩手向前徐徐散</l><l>當知已繫無垢繒</l></lg>
<lb n="0707b07"/><p>真言曰</p>
<lb n="0707b08"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>囉怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>莽&CB00619;鼻曬計囉鼻詵
<lb n="0707b09"/>者娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00805;薩&CB00085;母捺囉<note place="inline">二合</note>冥涅哩<note place="inline">二合</note>雉
<lb n="0707b10"/>句嚕&CB00085;囉迦&CB00085;制娜&CB00680;</p>
<lb n="0707b11"/><lg><l>次結寶劍自灌頂</l><l>二手合掌屈進力</l>
<lb n="0707b12"/><l>禪智皆屈入掌中</l><l>置於額上分兩邊</l></lg>
<lb n="0707b13"/><p>灌頂真言曰</p>
<lb n="0707b14"/><p type="dharani">唵囉怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>俱舍仡哩耶<note place="inline">三合</note>吽<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0707b15"/><lg><l>次復結於甲冑印</l><l>二手皆作金剛拳</l>
<lb n="0707b16"/><l>置於心前&CB00594;進力</l><l>左右二度想唵砧</l>
<lb n="0707b17"/><l>想流清光為綠色</l><l>心前三轉遶背後</l>
<lb n="0707b18"/><l>復至臍下及兩膝</l><l>又轉至臍遶腰後</l>
<lb n="0707b19"/><l>從腰到心轉兩膊</l><l>從膊至喉向頸後</l>
<lb n="0707b20"/><l>復從頸後至額前</l><l>從額至腦結智拳</l>
<lb n="0707b21"/><l>徐徐散下如垂帶</l><l><note n="0707008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上＝止【乙】</note><app n="0707008"><lem>上</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">止</rdg></app>觀旋轉如舞勢</l>
<lb n="0707b22"/><l>二手相叉成滿月</l></lg>
<lb n="0707b23"/><p>甲冑真言曰</p>
<lb n="0707b24"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>迦&CB00085;左&CB00085;日&CB00074;<note place="inline">二合</note>句嚕&CB00085;日囉
<lb n="0707b25"/><note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0707009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔娜〕－【乙】</note><app n="0707009"><lem>娜</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>含</p>
<lb n="0707b26"/><lg><l>次陳金剛拍掌儀</l><l>二羽齊拍<note n="0707010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一＝三【乙】</note><app n="0707010"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">三</rdg></app>相拍</l>
<lb n="0707b27"/><l>由陳拍印真言并</l><l>能令聖眾發歡喜</l>
<lb n="0707b28"/><l>速獲本尊堅固體</l></lg>
<lb n="0707b29"/><p>歡喜真言曰</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1171.0707c" n="0707c"/>
<lb n="0707c01"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底<note place="inline">引</note>乞叉拏<note place="inline">三合</note>&CB00418;使野<note place="inline">二合</note>斛<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0707c02"/><lg><l>次當行者座前觀</l><l>八葉蓮花具鬚&CB00610;</l>
<lb n="0707c03"/><l>上觀師子妙高座</l><l>座上復有七寶樓</l>
<lb n="0707c04"/><l>中想七寶蓮花王</l><l>上想曇字具威<note n="0707011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">光＝德【乙】</note><app n="0707011"><lem>光</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">德</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0707c05"/><l>遍照法界靡不周</l><l>其字變為金剛利</l>
<lb n="0707c06"/><l>了了諦觀如本形</l><l>召請菩薩入想身</l>
<lb n="0707c07"/><l>二手作月進如鉤</l><l>想身同於彼菩薩</l></lg>
<lb n="0707c08"/><p>金剛鉤菩薩真言曰</p>
<lb n="0707c09"/><p type="dharani">唵阿夜<note place="inline">引</note>呬弱</p>
<lb n="0707c10"/><lg><l>次當結索入尊身</l><l>結月禪押智入掌</l>
<lb n="0707c11"/><l>由此密印加持故</l><l>變為一體無有差</l></lg>
<lb n="0707c12"/><p>金剛索真言曰</p>
<lb n="0707c13"/><p type="dharani">唵阿呬吽吽</p>
<lb n="0707c14"/><lg><l>次當鎖印令堅固</l><l>作月四度猶如環</l>
<lb n="0707c15"/><l>由此祕印威力故</l><l>悉令堅固而不變</l></lg>
<lb n="0707c16"/><p>金剛鎖真言曰</p>
<lb n="0707c17"/><p type="dharani">唵係娑普<note place="inline">二合</note>吒<note n="0707012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00680;＝&CB00805;【乙】</note><app n="0707012"><lem>&CB00680;</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00805;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0707c18"/><lg><l>次結鈴印令歡喜</l><l>禪智八掌如鈴鐸</l>
<lb n="0707c19"/><l>令尊及眾皆歡喜</l><l>加持令速妙成就</l></lg>
<lb n="0707c20"/><p>金剛鈴真言曰</p>
<lb n="0707c21"/><p type="dharani">唵健吒噁噁</p>
<lb n="0707c22"/><p>行者次當兩手捧遏伽想洗金剛利菩薩及諸
<lb n="0707c23"/>眷屬<note n="0707013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">足＝之【乙】</note><app n="0707013"><lem>足</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">之</rdg></app>。或以百字真言加持遏伽。而獻遏伽
<lb n="0707c24"/>真言曰</p>
<lb n="0707c25"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日<note n="0707014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盧二合＝嚧【乙】</note><app n="0707014"><lem>盧<note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">嚧</rdg></app>娜迦吽<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0707c26"/><lg><l>次結曼殊羯磨印</l><l>二羽皆作金剛拳</l>
<lb n="0707c27"/><l>禪羽置於自心上</l><l>右手猶如執劍勢</l>
<lb n="0707c28"/><l>由此羯<anchor id="fxT20p0707c01"/>麼妙印力</l><l>身獲如尊等無異</l></lg>
<lb n="0707c29"/><p>羯<anchor id="fxT20p0707c02"/>麼真言曰</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1171.0708a" n="0708a"/>
<lb n="0708a01"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底乞叉拏<note place="inline">三合</note>曇</p>
<lb n="0708a02"/><lg><l>次結金剛利劍印</l><l>結月忍願申如劍</l>
<lb n="0708a03"/><l>由此金剛利妙印</l><l>當獲般若甚深智</l></lg>
<lb n="0708a04"/><p>金剛利真言曰</p>
<lb n="0708a05"/><p type="dharani">唵耨佉泚娜</p>
<lb n="0708a06"/><lg><l>次復當結內供養</l><l>結月當心&CB00594;禪智</l>
<lb n="0708a07"/><l>由結金剛<note n="0708001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嬉＝喜【乙】＊</note><app n="0708001"><lem>嬉</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">喜</rdg></app>戲印</l><l>速滿檀那波羅蜜</l></lg>
<lb n="0708a08"/><p>金剛<anchor id="fxT20p0708a01"/>嬉戲真言曰</p>
<lb n="0708a09"/><p type="dharani">唵摩訶囉底</p>
<lb n="0708a10"/><lg><l>次結金剛鬘供養</l><l>依前<anchor id="fxT20p0708a02"/>嬉戲直申臂</l>
<lb n="0708a11"/><l>由結此印加持故</l><l>當滿淨戒波羅密</l></lg>
<lb n="0708a12"/><p>金剛鬘真言曰</p>
<lb n="0708a13"/><p type="dharani">唵嚕跛戍<note place="inline">引</note>鞞</p>
<lb n="0708a14"/><lg><l>次結金剛歌詠印</l><l>鬘至臍口垂下散</l>
<lb n="0708a15"/><l>由結金剛歌密印</l><l>速獲安忍波羅蜜</l></lg>
<lb n="0708a16"/><p>金剛歌真言曰</p>
<lb n="0708a17"/><p type="dharani">唵戍嚕<note place="inline">二合</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>掃磎</p>
<lb n="0708a18"/><lg><l>次結金剛舞供養</l><l>二手拳旋如舞勢</l>
<lb n="0708a19"/><l>由結舞印加持<note n="0708002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">故＝力【乙】</note><app n="0708002"><lem>故</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">力</rdg></app></l><l>速滿精進波羅蜜</l></lg>
<lb n="0708a20"/><p>金剛舞印真言曰</p>
<lb n="0708a21"/><p type="dharani">唵薩&CB00085;布爾</p>
<lb n="0708a22"/><lg><l>次結金剛外供養</l><l>二手作月向下散</l>
<lb n="0708a23"/><l>由結燒香印力故</l><l>當證靜慮波羅蜜</l></lg>
<lb n="0708a24"/><p>金剛燒香真言曰</p>
<lb n="0708a25"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>賀&CB00256;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00135;<note place="inline">引</note>寧<note place="inline">上</note></p>
<lb n="0708a26"/><lg><l>次結金剛散花印</l><l>結月向上如散花</l>
<lb n="0708a27"/><l>由此散花印加持</l><l>速證般若波羅蜜</l></lg>
<lb n="0708a28"/><p>金剛散花真言曰</p>
<lb n="0708a29"/><p type="dharani">唵頗&CB00256;<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00344;銘</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1171.0708b" n="0708b"/>
<lb n="0708b01"/><lg><l>次結金剛燈明印</l><l>作月禪智頭相著</l>
<lb n="0708b02"/><l>由結金剛燈明印</l><l>當得方便波羅蜜</l></lg>
<lb n="0708b03"/><p>金剛燈明真言曰</p>
<lb n="0708b04"/><p type="dharani"><anchor id="fxT20p0708b01"/>奄蘇帝惹<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00617;哩<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0708b05"/><lg><l>次結金剛塗香印</l><l>月當胸散如塗香</l>
<lb n="0708b06"/><l>由結塗香印加持</l><l>速滿誓願波羅蜜</l></lg>
<lb n="0708b07"/><p>金剛塗香真言曰</p>
<lb n="0708b08"/><p type="dharani">唵蘇健蕩倪<note place="inline">倪以<note n="0708003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔兮〕－【乙】</note><app n="0708003"><lem>兮</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>反</note></p>
<lb n="0708b09"/><p>行者次應誦一百八名讚供養本尊。又結金
<lb n="0708b10"/>剛利劍印。於心上誦百字真言加持自身。假
<lb n="0708b11"/>使過去世中造種種惡業五無間等一切罪
<lb n="0708b12"/>障。由此百字真言加持故。一切罪障悉皆消
<lb n="0708b13"/>滅。見身獲得首楞嚴三昧。若心散亂數誦此
<lb n="0708b14"/>明或一七三七乃至七七一百八遍。心離攀
<lb n="0708b15"/>緣速得三摩地</p>
<lb n="0708b16"/><p>百字真言</p>
<lb n="0708b17"/><p type="dharani">唵渴&CB00344;薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合一</note>三麼耶麼努播<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00256;耶<note place="inline"><note n="0708004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【乙】</note><app n="0708004"><lem>二合</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0708b18"/>二</note>渴&CB00344;薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline"><note n="0708005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二合三＝三二合【乙】</note><app n="0708005"><lem>二合三</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">三二合</rdg></app></note>底吠<note place="inline">二合</note>怒跛底瑟&CB00109;<note place="inline">二合四</note>
<lb n="0708b19"/>涅哩<note place="inline">二合</note>住<note place="inline"><note n="0708006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">茶＝荼【乙】</note><app n="0708006"><lem>茶</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">荼</rdg></app>護反</note>銘婆<note place="inline"><note n="0708007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">去＝上【乙】</note><app n="0708007"><lem>去</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">上</rdg></app></note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">五</note>素&CB00418;使喻<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0708b20"/>銘婆<note place="inline">去</note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">六</note>阿<note place="inline">上</note><note n="0708008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拏＝努【乙】</note><app n="0708008"><lem>拏</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">努</rdg></app>囉訖&CB00418;<note place="inline">二合</note>銘婆<note place="inline">去</note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">七</note>素
<lb n="0708b21"/>布使喻<note place="inline">二合引</note>銘婆<note place="inline">去</note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">八</note>薩&CB00085;悉朕<note place="inline">提飲反</note>銘&CB00425;囉
<lb n="0708b22"/><note place="inline">二合</note>也瑳<note place="inline">九</note>薩&CB00085;羯磨素者銘<note place="inline">十</note>質多失唎<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0708b23"/>藥句嚕<note place="inline">十一</note>吽<note place="inline">引</note>訶訶訶訶斛<note place="inline">引</note>婆&CB00344;&CB00680;<note place="inline">十二</note>薩
<lb n="0708b24"/>&CB00085;怛他&CB00617;多<note place="inline">十三</note>渴&CB00344;麼銘門<note place="inline">上</note>者<note n="0708009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔十四〕－【乙】</note><app n="0708009"><lem><note place="inline">十四</note></lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>渴倪
<lb n="0708b25"/><note place="inline">倪以反</note>婆&CB00085;<note place="inline">十五</note><anchor id="fxT20p0708b02"/>摩訶三摩耶薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>惡<note place="inline">引十六</note></p>
<lb n="0708b26"/><p>不散前印。諦觀前有本尊。及想自身如本尊
<lb n="0708b27"/>無異。了了諦觀即誦五字陀羅尼。或以金剛
<lb n="0708b28"/>語誦。<note n="0708010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">或＝我【乙】</note><app n="0708010"><lem>或</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">我</rdg></app>分明蓮華語誦。或誦七遍三七遍。
<lb n="0708b29"/>以印於頂上解散。次即把念珠當心念誦不
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1171.0708c" n="0708c"/>
<lb n="0708c01"/>緩不急。或一百八遍或一千乃至一萬遍。念
<lb n="0708c02"/>誦數畢。二手<note n="0708011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">捧＝棒【乙】</note><app n="0708011"><lem>捧</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">棒</rdg></app>珠安於頂上。然後置本處。
<lb n="0708c03"/>若三摩地念誦者。當心觀大圓鏡智。中布
<lb n="0708c04"/>五字門。了了諦觀。隨義相應。心與般若波羅
<lb n="0708c05"/>蜜合。此名三摩地念誦。若身疲懈。即結本尊
<lb n="0708c06"/>劍印。誦五字陀羅尼七遍。復以八大供養供
<lb n="0708c07"/>養諸佛。以妙音辭稱揚讚歎。獻閼伽水。以降
<lb n="0708c08"/>三世印左旋解界。即結金剛利劍印。奉送諸
<lb n="0708c09"/>聖。各還本宮。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0708c10"/><p type="dharani">唵訖哩<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00418;<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">無莫反一</note>薩&CB00085;薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>囉他
<lb n="0708c11"/><note place="inline">二合二</note>悉地捺多<note place="inline">引三</note>也他<note place="inline">引</note>努&CB00344;<note place="inline"><note n="0708012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引上四＝上四引【乙】</note><app n="0708012"><lem>引上四</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">上四引</rdg></app></note>&CB00617;縒<note n="0708013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">持＝特【乙】</note><app n="0708013"><lem>持</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">特</rdg></app>
<lb n="0708c12"/>挽<note place="inline">二合</note>沒馱尾灑焰<note place="inline">五</note>布曩囉<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00344;<note place="inline">六</note>麼囊<note place="inline">引</note>也
<lb n="0708c13"/>都<note place="inline">七</note>唵渴&CB00344;薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>目<note place="inline">八</note></p>
<lb n="0708c14"/><p>作此法已。重以三麼耶印誦加持明以印四
<lb n="0708c15"/>處。然後灌頂。被金<note n="0708014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔剛〕－【乙】</note><app n="0708014"><lem>剛</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>甲冑。依前四禮禮四
<lb n="0708c16"/>方佛。懺悔發願等。然後依閑靜處。嚴以香花
<lb n="0708c17"/>住本尊三摩地。讀誦方廣一切大乘經典大
<lb n="0708c18"/>般若大品。乃至文殊般若等。隨意經行</p>
<lb n="0708c19"/><lg><l>若有智者依<note n="0708015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此＋（教）【乙】</note><app n="0708015"><lem>此</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">此教</rdg></app>法</l><l>晝夜四時精進修</l>
<lb n="0708c20"/><l><note n="0708016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見＝現【乙】</note><app n="0708016"><lem>見</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">現</rdg></app>世證得歡喜地</l><l>後十六生成正覺</l></lg>
<lb n="0708c21"/><note n="0708017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔文殊…二合〕百二十九字－【乙】</note><app n="0708017" word-count="129"><lem><p>文殊師利忿怒陀羅尼</p>
<lb n="0708c22"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底乞叉拏<note place="inline">三合</note>俱嚕<note place="inline">二合</note>馱瞋那
<lb n="0708c23"/>瞋那吽<note place="inline">引</note>泮吒</p>
<lb n="0708c24"/><p>用此真言護身辟除結界。淨諸香花及一切
<lb n="0708c25"/>供具等並得</p>
<lb n="0708c26"/><lg><l>當願眾生遇此教</l><l>曼殊常為善知識</l>
<lb n="0708c27"/><l>速證般若善巧智</l><l>疾成無上兩足尊</l></lg>
<lb n="0708c28"/><p>五字陀羅尼</p>
<lb n="0708c29"/><p type="dharani">阿囉跛者曩唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底乞叉拏<note place="inline">三合</note>唵耨
